               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Taʾāmra Māryām “Miracles of Mary” (fols. 3ra-1979va)&#xD;
I-1) Maṣḥafa śǝrʿāt, The rite of al-Muʿallaqah (fols. 3ra-8rb)&#xD;
I-2) Introductory exhortation (fols. 8rb-11rb)&#xD;
I-3) ʾƎsaggǝd laki wa-ʾǝweddǝsäkki... “I worship Thee…” (fols. 11rb-12rb)&#xD;
I-4) Taʾāmra Māryām: 162 miracles (fols. 12rb-225rb)&#xD;
I-5) ʾAkkonu bǝʾǝsi... "Does not the man..." (fols. 149va-179va, distributed among the Miracles of Mary).</summary>
